<h2>About Us</h2>
<div class="float-container">

  <div class="float-child-1">
    <div class="white"><h3>1. Who are we ?</h3></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="float-child-2">
    <div class="black"><h4>We are the students in University of Houston, aspired to learn software design by hands-on experience under the guidance of Professor Amin Alipuri.
      As part of the course work, we come up with the project of a website where students can easily find roommates and review the rental places.
    </h4></div>
  </div>
  
</div>
<div class="float-container">

  <div class="float-child-1">
    <div class="white"><h3>2. What is Homeify ?</h3></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="float-child-2">
    <div class="black"><h4> Homeify is a platform to help college students 
      who are searching for people with similar interests and can get genuine reviews on existing rental places. 
      This website allows students to connect with various people by sharing their interests and thoughts on the renting places,
       so that they can be free from the hurdle of finding people whenever they are moving to new places.</h4></div>
  </div>
  <div class="float-container">

  <div class="float-child-1">
    <div class="white"><h3>3. How is Homeify different from others ?</h3></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="float-child-2">
    <div class="black"><h4>Homeify provides you a platform to not just find people, 
      it gives you a feature to find people with same college and looking for similar rental places. 
      The post feature allows you to share your views on what kind of places 
      you're looking for and what you're expecting from your roomies which is something we all wanna do if ever we had a chance.</h4></div>
  </div>
  
</div>
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="row">
      
        <div class="col-lg-12">
